We know that by choosing DigitalOcean, you value simplicity, peace of mind, and flexibility.

We understand that no matter your business needs, you need to be able to scale quickly, sleep well at night knowing your infrastructure is secure and reliable, and most of all have the flexibility to pivot quickly and achieve your goals. At DigitalOcean, there are plenty of starting points to choose from that offer flexibility, support, and most of all peace of mind. All that’s left to do is decide which of our offerings serve your business best:

[Droplets](https://www.digitalocean.com/products/droplets)

Spin up virtual machine configurations sized for any app. Droplets come in multiple vCPU and RAM configurations and provide a generous amount of SSD storage and bandwidth. Pro tip: speaking of peace of mind, enable Backups to automatically create disk images of your Droplet and revert to a previous state with a single click.

[Get started with Droplets >](https://www.digitalocean.com/products/droplets)

[Marketplace 1-Clicks](https://marketplace.digitalocean.com/)

Our 1-Click Droplets are deployed in seconds and save time with preconfigured environments that already have all the prerequisites installed. From Wordpress to LAMP, Jitsi, and more, we have hundreds of 1-Clicks to choose from.

[Get started with 1-Clicks >](https://marketplace.digitalocean.com/)

[Spaces](https://www.digitalocean.com/products/spaces)

DigitalOcean Spaces makes it simple to store your data at any scale, with a powerful API and built-in Content Delivery Network (CDN). Spaces can support 800 total operations per second, making all of the images and data essential to your business immediately available.

[Get started with Spaces >](https://www.digitalocean.com/products/spaces)

[Managed Databases](https://www.digitalocean.com/products/managed-databases)

All of your data stored in one place, immediately accessible, and most importantly, separate from your networking needs? Consider using Managed Database clusters which include daily backups, standby nodes for high availability, and end-to-end SSL encryption.

[Get started with Managed Databases >](https://www.digitalocean.com/products/managed-databases)

